1
00:01:49,060 --> 00:01:54,580
=Eight Hundred=

2
00:01:57,180 --> 00:01:58,980
(Yingxiong Roller Skating Rink)

3
00:01:58,980 --> 00:02:00,850
♪Today, I♪

4
00:02:02,340 --> 00:02:05,280
♪Watch the snow
drift by in the cold night♪

5
00:02:05,600 --> 00:02:10,250
♪Drifting afar with a chilled heart♪

6
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:14,220
♪Chasing in the wind and rain♪

7
00:02:14,540 --> 00:02:17,540
♪Unable to distinguish
shadows in the mist♪

8
00:02:17,540 --> 00:02:20,540
♪The wide sea and sky, you and I♪

9
00:02:20,850 --> 00:02:23,980
♪Could we change? Who isn't changing?♪

10
00:02:23,980 --> 00:02:25,950
♪How many times♪

11
00:02:27,180 --> 00:02:28,020
Thanks.

12
00:02:28,020 --> 00:02:28,860
Han Ning.

13
00:02:28,860 --> 00:02:29,700
You're here.

14
00:02:30,880 --> 00:02:32,520
Boss, give me two bottles of Jianlibao.

15
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:33,390
Alright.

16
00:02:38,160 --> 00:02:39,030
Thank you.

17
00:02:39,030 --> 00:02:39,890
You're welcome.

18
00:02:41,290 --> 00:02:42,890
It's so crowded today.

19
00:02:45,550 --> 00:02:49,190
♪The love in my heart,
who understands me?♪

20
00:02:49,190 --> 00:02:55,300
♪Forgive me for being wild
and unfettered my whole life♪

21
00:02:56,180 --> 00:03:00,900
♪I'm also afraid
that one day I might fall♪

22
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:04,400
♪Forsaking my ideals♪

23
00:03:04,760 --> 00:03:07,740
♪Anyone can do that♪

24
00:03:08,720 --> 00:03:14,890
♪What's there to fear
if one day it's just you and me?♪

25
00:03:34,860 --> 00:03:35,700
Chief Liu.

26
00:03:39,020 --> 00:03:39,860
You're here.

27
00:03:42,260 --> 00:03:43,120
Chief Liu.

28
00:03:43,120 --> 00:03:44,300
I'm here to report on my work.

29
00:03:45,700 --> 00:03:46,790
Chief Liu, why are you...

30
00:03:47,380 --> 00:03:49,300
Chief Liu, what's wrong with you?

31
00:04:02,980 --> 00:04:03,820
(Yingxiong Roller Skating Rink)
Watch out.

32
00:04:04,300 --> 00:04:05,630
Thank you, everyone.

33
00:04:10,940 --> 00:04:12,100
Thank you.

34
00:04:13,020 --> 00:04:14,100
Next, I'm going

35
00:04:14,100 --> 00:04:15,980
to perform another song for you.

36
00:04:15,980 --> 00:04:17,500
I hope you'll like it.

37
00:04:17,500 --> 00:04:18,730
I also wish you all

38
00:04:18,730 --> 00:04:20,260
a great time here today.

39
00:04:29,540 --> 00:04:33,420
=Episode 4=
(The Chain Trap)

40
00:04:33,540 --> 00:04:36,940
(Fengyang Coal Mine Guesthouse)

41
00:04:39,620 --> 00:04:40,620
Chief Liu,

42
00:04:41,300 --> 00:04:42,140
quick, look.

43
00:04:42,660 --> 00:04:43,860
What is she trying to say?

44
00:04:43,860 --> 00:04:45,610
She's this sick,
why don't you take her to the hospital?

45
00:04:45,610 --> 00:04:47,010
I can't manage all by myself.

46
00:04:47,620 --> 00:04:49,530
I only think
of finding you when someone's sick.

47
00:04:49,530 --> 00:04:51,040
I never think of going to the hospital.

48
00:04:51,050 --> 00:04:52,150
Hold this, hold it higher.

49
00:05:26,180 --> 00:05:27,460
Didn't we agree

50
00:05:27,780 --> 00:05:28,940
that if I gave you the stuff,

51
00:05:28,940 --> 00:05:29,900
you would leave?

52
00:05:31,500 --> 00:05:32,530
I intended to leave.

53
00:05:33,580 --> 00:05:34,420
I got robbed.

54
00:05:36,860 --> 00:05:37,900
So what do you want?

55
00:05:41,340 --> 00:05:42,220
What else?

56
00:05:43,220 --> 00:05:44,180
Give me some more money.

57
00:05:44,900 --> 00:05:45,900
And some more drugs.

58
00:05:52,980 --> 00:05:53,940
I don't hit women.

59
00:05:54,320 --> 00:05:55,790
Tell your Chen Hui to get over here.

60
00:05:56,140 --> 00:05:57,140
Cut the crap with me.

61
00:05:57,140 --> 00:05:58,240
What are you trying to do?

62
00:05:58,260 --> 00:05:59,550
What else would I do?

63
00:05:59,900 --> 00:06:01,980
Fifty thousand yuan
and five bottles of drugs.

64
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:04,220
It was fifty thousand last time,
and another fifty thousand now?

65
00:06:04,220 --> 00:06:05,220
Are you crazy?

66
00:06:05,220 --> 00:06:06,520
We can't give you fifty thousand.

67
00:06:06,860 --> 00:06:07,830
I'm crazy?

68
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:10,410
When you tried
to blow me up with detonators,

69
00:06:10,420 --> 00:06:11,540
weren't you pretty crazy too?

70
00:06:12,260 --> 00:06:13,980
Who are you trying to scare, anyway?

71
00:06:13,980 --> 00:06:16,110
Listen here, get the money ready
for me quickly.

72
00:06:19,380 --> 00:06:20,300
You even have a knife?

73
00:06:21,540 --> 00:06:22,400
Going to stab me?

74
00:06:22,540 --> 00:06:23,380
Come on.

75
00:06:23,660 --> 00:06:24,500
Stab me.

76
00:06:24,740 --> 00:06:25,580
Come on.

77
00:06:25,580 --> 00:06:26,420
Stab me, come on.

78
00:06:26,620 --> 00:06:27,460
Come on.

79
00:06:27,620 --> 00:06:28,940
Weren't you capable? Stab me then.

80
00:06:30,340 --> 00:06:31,580
Why the heck did you come back?

81
00:06:32,660 --> 00:06:33,500
I was robbed.

82
00:06:35,860 --> 00:06:38,300
Get another fifty thousand yuan ready,
plus five bottles of drugs.

83
00:06:38,300 --> 00:06:39,410
I'll come to pick them up tomorrow.

84
00:06:40,540 --> 00:06:42,860
Otherwise, you know what will happen.

85
00:06:50,340 --> 00:06:51,180
How are you?

86
00:06:51,660 --> 00:06:52,500
Are you okay?

87
00:06:54,020 --> 00:06:55,060
Lu Yuan has gone mad.

88
00:06:55,590 --> 00:06:56,450
Give me the knife.

89
00:06:56,780 --> 00:06:57,620
Give me the knife.

90
00:07:03,460 --> 00:07:04,300
It's okay.

91
00:07:04,540 --> 00:07:05,380
It's okay.

92
00:07:05,980 --> 00:07:06,820
Everything's fine.

93
00:07:07,340 --> 00:07:08,180
I'm here.

94
00:07:08,900 --> 00:07:09,810
I'm here.

95
00:07:10,330 --> 00:07:11,170
It's over now.

96
00:07:28,620 --> 00:07:29,660
You are...

97
00:07:29,660 --> 00:07:30,670
Your fever has broken.

98
00:07:31,180 --> 00:07:32,300
Rest a bit longer.

99
00:07:36,940 --> 00:07:38,350
Did you set up the IV for me?

100
00:07:39,020 --> 00:07:40,390
I am Chen Hongbing's wife.

101
00:07:40,630 --> 00:07:41,550
My name is Ding Yue.

102
00:07:41,820 --> 00:07:42,700
I'm a doctor.

103
00:07:45,580 --> 00:07:46,420
Chief Liu,

104
00:07:46,420 --> 00:07:47,260
you're awake?

105
00:07:47,260 --> 00:07:48,120
Director Chen.

106
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:48,980
Are you feeling better?

107
00:07:48,980 --> 00:07:49,820
Much better.

108
00:07:49,830 --> 00:07:51,010
Her fever has already broken.

109
00:07:51,220 --> 00:07:52,060
That's great.

110
00:07:52,340 --> 00:07:53,180
Oh, right.

111
00:07:53,180 --> 00:07:54,860
I couldn't find
any fruit for sale tonight.

112
00:07:54,860 --> 00:07:57,500
Back at home, I searched for ages
and only found these two cucumbers.

113
00:07:57,500 --> 00:07:58,390
So I brought them over.

114
00:07:58,540 --> 00:07:59,380
Honestly,

115
00:07:59,380 --> 00:08:01,260
how are you even running the station?

116
00:08:01,350 --> 00:08:03,100
Aren't those cabarets and bathhouses

117
00:08:03,100 --> 00:08:04,870
always selling fruit platters?

118
00:08:04,870 --> 00:08:06,100
Look at how you handled this.

119
00:08:06,100 --> 00:08:07,210
It's fine, really.

120
00:08:07,690 --> 00:08:08,540
I'm not hungry.

121
00:08:08,820 --> 00:08:10,220
Even if you aren't, you need to eat.

122
00:08:10,220 --> 00:08:12,510
Chen Hongbing called me over
in such a frantic rush.

123
00:08:12,820 --> 00:08:13,690
Since I didn't know

124
00:08:13,690 --> 00:08:15,460
if you were allergic to penicillin,

125
00:08:15,460 --> 00:08:16,910
I gave you an IV of azithromycin.

126
00:08:17,130 --> 00:08:18,920
This medication is hard on the stomach.

127
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:20,000
Eat something,

128
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,120
and you won't feel so sick.

129
00:08:21,420 --> 00:08:22,260
Exactly.

130
00:08:22,260 --> 00:08:23,100
Listen to my wife.

131
00:08:23,420 --> 00:08:25,110
You need to put
something in your stomach.

132
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:27,450
Honey,

133
00:08:27,580 --> 00:08:28,580
I have to thank you.

134
00:08:28,580 --> 00:08:30,080
It's all thanks to you tonight.

135
00:08:30,180 --> 00:08:31,300
We're an old married couple,

136
00:08:31,300 --> 00:08:32,460
so why the formality?

137
00:08:32,460 --> 00:08:33,730
Go wash those cucumbers.

138
00:08:33,860 --> 00:08:34,700
Yes.

139
00:08:37,510 --> 00:08:39,330
You and Director Chen
are quite affectionate.

140
00:08:40,280 --> 00:08:41,640
Thank you for today, Mrs. Chen.

141
00:08:42,870 --> 00:08:44,460
Well, you came to Fengyang alone,

142
00:08:44,640 --> 00:08:46,500
and you're a stranger in a new place.

143
00:08:46,500 --> 00:08:47,570
Doing this for you

144
00:08:47,660 --> 00:08:48,710
is the least we can do.

145
00:08:49,140 --> 00:08:50,110
But

146
00:08:50,400 --> 00:08:52,970
being away from home for so long,

147
00:08:53,380 --> 00:08:55,220
doesn't your husband worry about you?

148
00:08:57,700 --> 00:08:58,690
I'm divorced.

149
00:08:59,260 --> 00:09:00,220
Oh, look at me,

150
00:09:00,430 --> 00:09:02,070
asking things I shouldn't have.

151
00:09:02,460 --> 00:09:03,470
It's okay.

152
00:09:03,710 --> 00:09:04,610
I'm sorry.

153
00:09:04,610 --> 00:09:05,460
Please get some rest.

154
00:09:05,620 --> 00:09:06,550
I'll pack up my things.

155
00:09:07,060 --> 00:09:07,900
Here,

156
00:09:08,980 --> 00:09:10,170
have some of this first.

157
00:09:12,340 --> 00:09:13,460
Have some cucumber first.

158
00:09:13,810 --> 00:09:14,720
Just leave it there.

159
00:09:15,470 --> 00:09:17,940
Director Chen, was there something specific

160
00:09:17,940 --> 00:09:19,110
you wanted to discuss this late?

161
00:09:20,440 --> 00:09:22,360
I wanted to talk about the case.

162
00:09:22,580 --> 00:09:23,490
Never mind.

163
00:09:23,490 --> 00:09:24,350
We'll talk tomorrow.

164
00:09:25,550 --> 00:09:26,620
I'm fine now.

165
00:09:27,110 --> 00:09:28,460
Did you find something new?

166
00:09:28,650 --> 00:09:29,940
Not exactly a new discovery,

167
00:09:30,030 --> 00:09:32,660
it's just that Yu Susu
is acting very strange.

168
00:09:32,780 --> 00:09:35,300
From chasing sugar daddies
to dealing with the cough syrup...

169
00:09:35,540 --> 00:09:37,080
Think about it. She doesn't lack money

170
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:38,060
or men.

171
00:09:38,220 --> 00:09:40,230
So why would she marry
a miner from an illegal pit?

172
00:09:40,950 --> 00:09:41,950
What is she after?

173
00:09:43,820 --> 00:09:44,860
You're right.

174
00:09:44,860 --> 00:09:46,420
When you piece it all together,

175
00:09:47,250 --> 00:09:48,820
Yu Susu surely has issues.

176
00:09:49,790 --> 00:09:51,820
Besides, Zhu Qiang has gone mad.

177
00:09:52,860 --> 00:09:54,620
Why do all these strange things

178
00:09:54,620 --> 00:09:56,580
happen around Yu Susu?

179
00:10:02,820 --> 00:10:03,660
Mrs. Chen.

180
00:10:04,340 --> 00:10:05,660
Are you feeling unwell?

181
00:10:05,660 --> 00:10:06,510
No.

182
00:10:06,510 --> 00:10:07,580
Let me ask you something.

183
00:10:08,100 --> 00:10:09,180
Can drinking cough syrup

184
00:10:09,310 --> 00:10:10,390
make someone go mad?

185
00:10:10,740 --> 00:10:12,700
Cough syrup alone won't.

186
00:10:12,890 --> 00:10:16,460
But if taken with stomach medicine,
it can easily affect one's mental state.

187
00:10:19,370 --> 00:10:20,210
Are you sure?

188
00:10:20,340 --> 00:10:21,820
Of course I am.

189
00:10:21,980 --> 00:10:24,800
When I worked at the Workers' Hospital,
most of what we handled

190
00:10:24,800 --> 00:10:26,040
were upper respiratory issues.

191
00:10:26,040 --> 00:10:27,400
I know the contraindications

192
00:10:27,400 --> 00:10:28,620
for cough syrup inside out.

193
00:10:28,840 --> 00:10:29,780
Director Chen,

194
00:10:29,970 --> 00:10:31,180
please make arrangements

195
00:10:31,210 --> 00:10:33,020
for the hospital
to take Zhu Qiang's blood.

196
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:35,410
I have to report back
to the municipal PSB tomorrow anyway.

197
00:10:35,690 --> 00:10:36,770
I'll take Zhu Qiang's blood

198
00:10:36,890 --> 00:10:37,950
directly there for testing.

199
00:10:38,020 --> 00:10:38,860
All right, will do.

200
00:10:38,860 --> 00:10:39,770
Don't worry.

201
00:10:39,770 --> 00:10:41,570
I'll have Limin arrange it tomorrow.

202
00:10:41,570 --> 00:10:42,420
Okay.

203
00:10:51,020 --> 00:10:53,300
Prepare another 50,000 yuan for me,
plus five bottles of medicine.

204
00:10:53,300 --> 00:10:54,260
I'll come to pick them up tomorrow.

205
00:10:54,260 --> 00:10:56,260
Otherwise, you know what will happen.

206
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:57,060
Have you got your things
and dialysis paperwork?

207
00:11:57,060 --> 00:11:58,300
Don't worry, I have everything.

208
00:11:59,690 --> 00:12:00,820
It's so early in the morning.

209
00:12:00,890 --> 00:12:02,220
Why have you started painting?

210
00:12:02,540 --> 00:12:03,940
I saw the wall was peeling,

211
00:12:04,040 --> 00:12:05,280
so I wanted to repaint it.

212
00:12:05,320 --> 00:12:07,110
Don't you have
an appointment with Lu Yuan later?

213
00:12:07,420 --> 00:12:08,350
It's just a small job.

214
00:12:08,350 --> 00:12:09,620
I'll be done before he arrives.

215
00:12:10,420 --> 00:12:11,810
I've got nothing else to do anyway.

216
00:12:12,230 --> 00:12:13,460
Just trying to distract myself.

217
00:12:15,620 --> 00:12:17,310
Let's just do what
we agreed on yesterday.

218
00:12:17,500 --> 00:12:18,460
Give him the money

219
00:12:18,460 --> 00:12:19,390
and settle the matter.

220
00:12:19,900 --> 00:12:21,570
If the money is gone, we can earn more.

221
00:12:21,740 --> 00:12:22,940
Don't be impulsive.

222
00:12:22,940 --> 00:12:23,870
Don't worry.

223
00:12:24,340 --> 00:12:25,330
You were right yesterday.

224
00:12:25,930 --> 00:12:26,780
We'll do as you said.

225
00:12:26,780 --> 00:12:27,620
All right?

226
00:12:28,820 --> 00:12:29,750
Director Chen.

227
00:12:29,750 --> 00:12:31,060
- Chief Liu.
- Chief Liu, let me take that.

228
00:12:31,060 --> 00:12:31,900
Thanks.

229
00:12:31,900 --> 00:12:33,380
Zhu Qiang's blood samples
are in the car.

230
00:12:33,380 --> 00:12:34,700
Good. When I get to the municipal PSB,

231
00:12:34,700 --> 00:12:35,670
I'll have Tang test them.

232
00:12:35,670 --> 00:12:36,850
Okay. Also,

233
00:12:37,300 --> 00:12:38,860
my wife told me to tell you

234
00:12:38,860 --> 00:12:40,220
to go to the municipal hospital

235
00:12:40,340 --> 00:12:41,620
and get a proper checkup.

236
00:12:43,390 --> 00:12:44,900
Fine. Thank her for me.

237
00:12:44,900 --> 00:12:46,180
Oh, I have something to tell you.

238
00:12:46,580 --> 00:12:48,620
Regarding Gao Ying's case,
give me the materials.

239
00:12:48,640 --> 00:12:50,910
On my way back to the municipal PSB,
I'll submit them for you

240
00:12:50,920 --> 00:12:52,610
to see if they can
be investigated together.

241
00:12:52,620 --> 00:12:53,460
Chief Liu,

242
00:12:53,570 --> 00:12:54,580
thank you so much.

243
00:12:54,580 --> 00:12:55,440
I've even put together

244
00:12:55,440 --> 00:12:56,710
some materials for this.

245
00:12:57,220 --> 00:12:58,560
They're at Hui's roller skating rink.

246
00:12:58,570 --> 00:12:59,660
Let's head over
and I'll get them for you.

247
00:12:59,660 --> 00:13:00,510
Sure, no problem.

248
00:13:00,510 --> 00:13:01,350
Let's go.

249
00:13:17,220 --> 00:13:18,060
Hello.

250
00:13:36,320 --> 00:13:37,710
What's wrong? Are you feeling unwell?

251
00:13:42,100 --> 00:13:43,300
Lie down first. Don't move.

252
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:44,530
I'll go get the doctor.

253
00:13:45,740 --> 00:13:46,690
Get him some tissues.

254
00:13:51,060 --> 00:13:52,180
It's so early in the morning.

255
00:13:52,330 --> 00:13:53,780
Why have you started painting?

256
00:13:53,780 --> 00:13:55,140
I saw the wall was peeling,

257
00:13:55,340 --> 00:13:56,510
so I wanted to repaint it.

258
00:13:56,520 --> 00:13:58,380
Don't you have an appointment
with Lu Yuan later?

259
00:13:58,380 --> 00:14:00,090
Let's just do
what we agreed on yesterday.

260
00:14:00,180 --> 00:14:01,140
Give him the money,

261
00:14:01,140 --> 00:14:02,220
and settle the matter.

262
00:14:02,340 --> 00:14:03,420
Don't be impulsive.

263
00:14:05,580 --> 00:14:06,420
Don't worry.

264
00:14:07,500 --> 00:14:08,580
You were right yesterday.

265
00:14:08,890 --> 00:14:09,760
We'll do as you said.

266
00:14:09,760 --> 00:14:10,610
All right?

267
00:14:13,450 --> 00:14:14,370
Miss,

268
00:14:14,370 --> 00:14:15,230
I'm not feeling well.

269
00:14:15,230 --> 00:14:16,180
I'll skip the dialysis for now.

270
00:14:16,180 --> 00:14:17,020
I'm leaving.

271
00:14:24,180 --> 00:14:25,450
Is the money and medicine ready?

272
00:14:25,740 --> 00:14:26,700
It's all on the bar.

273
00:14:26,700 --> 00:14:27,540
Count it yourself.

274
00:15:04,220 --> 00:15:05,060
Who is it?

275
00:15:06,100 --> 00:15:07,300
It's me, Hui.

276
00:15:08,900 --> 00:15:09,780
Coming!

277
00:15:14,500 --> 00:15:15,340
Warehouse.

278
00:15:15,780 --> 00:15:16,700
Hide in the warehouse.

279
00:15:26,980 --> 00:15:27,820
Dad.

280
00:15:27,820 --> 00:15:28,690
Hui,

281
00:15:28,690 --> 00:15:29,560
where did you put

282
00:15:29,560 --> 00:15:30,850
Aunt Gao Ying's iron box?

283
00:15:30,940 --> 00:15:31,810
It's in the warehouse.

284
00:15:32,120 --> 00:15:33,020
Bring it to me, quick.

285
00:15:33,020 --> 00:15:33,940
Dad,

286
00:15:33,940 --> 00:15:34,820
I'll go get it.

287
00:15:34,820 --> 00:15:35,660
Forget it.

288
00:15:35,660 --> 00:15:36,800
There's no light in the warehouse.

289
00:15:37,420 --> 00:15:38,260
You won't find it.

290
00:15:39,620 --> 00:15:40,460
Dad,

291
00:15:40,620 --> 00:15:41,540
let me get it for you.

292
00:15:41,540 --> 00:15:42,880
It's fine, I'll do it myself.

293
00:15:42,880 --> 00:15:43,720
Dad,

294
00:15:44,550 --> 00:15:45,710
you won't find it.

295
00:15:45,900 --> 00:15:46,740
Fine.

296
00:15:46,740 --> 00:15:47,740
Leave me alone.

297
00:15:53,460 --> 00:15:55,000
Dad!

298
00:15:55,500 --> 00:15:56,410
What's wrong?

299
00:15:56,620 --> 00:15:58,410
Look at the footprint
you left in the paint.

300
00:15:59,140 --> 00:16:00,460
What's going on with this?

301
00:16:00,460 --> 00:16:01,550
Just stay right there. Don't move.

302
00:16:01,550 --> 00:16:02,610
I'll bring it to you, okay?

303
00:16:03,340 --> 00:16:04,540
Hurry up.

304
00:16:04,540 --> 00:16:05,900
The car is waiting at the door.

305
00:16:17,100 --> 00:16:17,940
Okay.

306
00:16:18,580 --> 00:16:19,420
I'm heading out now.

307
00:16:19,420 --> 00:16:20,300
Clean this up quickly.

308
00:16:20,300 --> 00:16:21,140
I know.

309
00:16:22,180 --> 00:16:23,020
I'll see you out.

310
00:16:23,020 --> 00:16:23,860
No need.

311
00:16:25,860 --> 00:16:26,700
That's enough, Dad.

312
00:16:26,700 --> 00:16:27,540
Take it slow.

313
00:16:27,540 --> 00:16:28,380
Alright.

314
00:16:29,900 --> 00:16:32,460
Hui, there's something I need to tell you.

315
00:16:32,460 --> 00:16:33,420
What is it?

316
00:16:33,420 --> 00:16:35,300
Your mom's birthday is coming up.

317
00:16:35,300 --> 00:16:36,940
I want to get her a gift.

318
00:16:38,020 --> 00:16:39,660
Why the sudden thought of a gift?

319
00:16:39,940 --> 00:16:41,700
Your mom has been unhappy lately.

320
00:16:42,020 --> 00:16:43,180
We need to cheer her up.

321
00:16:44,040 --> 00:16:45,420
Help me think of what to get.

322
00:16:45,420 --> 00:16:46,300
Sure, I got it.

323
00:16:46,300 --> 00:16:48,100
I will tell you when I think of something.

324
00:16:48,780 --> 00:16:49,650
That's it then.

325
00:16:49,650 --> 00:16:50,560
Take care.

326
00:16:50,560 --> 00:16:51,400
Okay.

327
00:17:21,860 --> 00:17:22,700
Come out.

328
00:17:23,020 --> 00:17:27,060
(No Entry)

329
00:17:38,540 --> 00:17:39,380
Fifty thousand.

330
00:17:39,700 --> 00:17:40,580
I've counted it.

331
00:17:40,580 --> 00:17:41,660
Every cent is there.

332
00:17:42,700 --> 00:17:43,540
Thanks.

333
00:17:44,500 --> 00:17:45,540
Don't worry.

334
00:17:46,060 --> 00:17:47,890
I definitely won't be
coming back this time.

335
00:18:10,900 --> 00:18:12,940
Sir, could you please go a bit faster?

336
00:18:35,100 --> 00:18:35,940
Get lost!

337
00:18:39,100 --> 00:18:40,020
Call the police!

338
00:18:41,100 --> 00:18:42,020
Call the police!

339
00:18:42,620 --> 00:18:43,570
I want to make a report.

340
00:18:43,980 --> 00:18:44,820
What's going on?

341
00:18:45,120 --> 00:18:46,140
What are you shouting for?

342
00:18:46,140 --> 00:18:47,060
I want to make a report.

343
00:18:47,060 --> 00:18:48,400
You want to report something, right?

344
00:18:48,820 --> 00:18:49,660
Have a seat.

345
00:18:53,380 --> 00:18:54,920
Don't panic. Take your time.

346
00:18:54,920 --> 00:18:55,900
What exactly happened?

347
00:18:55,900 --> 00:18:57,100
- Just let me go, please!
- Sit back down!

348
00:18:57,100 --> 00:18:58,550
You've tested positive several times.

349
00:18:58,560 --> 00:19:00,180
Someone like you
gets at least three years.

350
00:19:00,180 --> 00:19:01,620
- Let's go.
- I'll change this time, I swear.

351
00:19:01,620 --> 00:19:02,460
I'll change.

352
00:19:05,810 --> 00:19:06,890
What are you looking at?

353
00:19:07,140 --> 00:19:08,210
What is wrong with you?

354
00:19:08,380 --> 00:19:09,420
I'm asking you a question.

355
00:19:09,500 --> 00:19:10,810
Weren't you reporting something?

356
00:19:11,220 --> 00:19:12,620
Why do you want to call the police?

357
00:19:22,740 --> 00:19:23,580
Dad.

358
00:19:24,140 --> 00:19:24,980
How did you get here?

359
00:19:25,620 --> 00:19:26,490
I came to find you.

360
00:19:26,820 --> 00:19:27,780
To find me?

361
00:19:27,780 --> 00:19:28,820
Come on in and let's talk.

362
00:19:29,060 --> 00:19:30,220
Let's talk here.

363
00:19:30,820 --> 00:19:31,690
Talk here?

364
00:19:31,690 --> 00:19:33,340
Look at you, covered in all this paint.

365
00:19:33,340 --> 00:19:34,180
What happened?

366
00:19:35,180 --> 00:19:36,580
I accidentally fell while painting.

367
00:19:36,580 --> 00:19:37,420
Got some on me.

368
00:19:38,540 --> 00:19:39,410
What is it?

369
00:19:40,020 --> 00:19:41,540
About what you mentioned before.

370
00:19:41,540 --> 00:19:42,380
I've been thinking.

371
00:19:43,140 --> 00:19:45,020
Doesn't Mom love watching
Demi-Gods and Semi-Devils?

372
00:19:45,700 --> 00:19:47,430
How about we buy her a DVD player?

373
00:19:47,860 --> 00:19:49,380
You came all the way here for that?

374
00:19:49,380 --> 00:19:50,540
Silly kid.

375
00:19:50,900 --> 00:19:52,820
Couldn't you have just called me?

376
00:19:52,820 --> 00:19:53,920
That would've worked, right?

377
00:19:54,340 --> 00:19:55,700
I was just about to go buy paint,

378
00:19:55,700 --> 00:19:57,040
so I thought I'd tell you in person.

379
00:19:57,050 --> 00:19:58,880
Things like this
are better discussed face-to-face.

380
00:19:59,700 --> 00:20:00,540
Director Chen.

381
00:20:02,260 --> 00:20:03,100
It's me.

382
00:20:08,540 --> 00:20:10,820
Aren't you the guy
I dragged into the urine test

383
00:20:11,180 --> 00:20:13,660
at the roller skating rink that night?

384
00:20:13,660 --> 00:20:14,500
Yeah, it's me.

385
00:20:14,500 --> 00:20:15,660
You little rascal,

386
00:20:15,660 --> 00:20:16,820
what are you doing here?

387
00:20:18,860 --> 00:20:19,700
Reporting something.

388
00:20:19,900 --> 00:20:20,740
Reporting something?

389
00:20:21,300 --> 00:20:22,220
What's the matter?

390
00:20:25,620 --> 00:20:27,140
I lost my ID card.

391
00:20:29,360 --> 00:20:31,150
You're calling the police
just for a lost ID?

392
00:20:31,150 --> 00:20:32,300
Wasn't I in a hurry?

393
00:20:32,300 --> 00:20:33,610
The people's police
for the people, right?

394
00:20:33,610 --> 00:20:34,470
That's enough.

395
00:20:34,470 --> 00:20:35,330
Get going.

396
00:20:35,340 --> 00:20:36,380
I'm leaving now, Director Chen.

397
00:20:36,380 --> 00:20:37,220
Go.

398
00:20:37,220 --> 00:20:38,300
Is this your son?

399
00:20:38,620 --> 00:20:39,460
What about it?

400
00:20:41,460 --> 00:20:42,340
He's handsome.

401
00:20:42,340 --> 00:20:43,460
Quite a talented young man.

402
00:20:44,340 --> 00:20:45,700
He looks just like you.

403
00:20:45,700 --> 00:20:47,100
Just go.

404
00:20:47,780 --> 00:20:49,540
Dad, I'll be heading out now.

405
00:20:49,540 --> 00:20:50,380
Alright.

406
00:20:51,780 --> 00:20:52,880
Go change your clothes.

407
00:20:53,660 --> 00:20:54,900
I know.

408
00:20:54,900 --> 00:20:55,740
Wait a second.

409
00:21:00,060 --> 00:21:00,980
Then,

410
00:21:00,980 --> 00:21:01,850
just like you said,

411
00:21:01,850 --> 00:21:03,900
go and buy a DVD player for your mother.

412
00:21:04,860 --> 00:21:05,700
Okay.

413
00:21:37,120 --> 00:21:38,820
You're quite something,
trying to kill me.

414
00:21:38,820 --> 00:21:39,940
You... Kill...

415
00:21:40,340 --> 00:21:41,220
Just now,

416
00:21:41,220 --> 00:21:42,530
you were quite something.

417
00:21:42,940 --> 00:21:43,820
Trying to kill me?

418
00:21:43,820 --> 00:21:44,660
Kill?

419
00:21:45,900 --> 00:21:47,260
Have you ever killed anyone?

420
00:21:47,260 --> 00:21:48,620
If you've got the guts,
go in and kill me.

421
00:21:48,620 --> 00:21:50,040
If your dad knew
his son was dealing drugs,

422
00:21:50,040 --> 00:21:51,190
what would he think?

423
00:21:51,190 --> 00:21:52,920
Where's the dignity
of the police station?

424
00:21:53,150 --> 00:21:54,430
But you didn't report it either.

425
00:21:54,720 --> 00:21:56,180
If you speak up, you're finished too.

426
00:21:59,460 --> 00:22:00,330
Listen here.

427
00:22:00,940 --> 00:22:02,140
I've changed my mind.

428
00:22:02,700 --> 00:22:04,040
Get 100,000 ready for me.

429
00:22:04,300 --> 00:22:05,340
You want 100,000?

430
00:22:05,530 --> 00:22:06,610
Ten thousand yuan.

431
00:22:06,700 --> 00:22:08,250
Not a penny less.

432
00:22:08,980 --> 00:22:10,890
If you're short,
prepare to rot in prison.

433
00:22:11,180 --> 00:22:13,280
If I end up inside,
don't even think about escaping.

434
00:22:13,540 --> 00:22:14,380
Fine.

435
00:22:14,540 --> 00:22:16,180
My life in exchange for both of yours.

436
00:22:16,180 --> 00:22:17,050
It's worth it.

437
00:22:17,050 --> 00:22:18,340
I wonder if that invalid of yours

438
00:22:18,340 --> 00:22:19,780
would even survive in there.

439
00:22:20,980 --> 00:22:22,220
Don't you touch Songge.

440
00:22:28,420 --> 00:22:29,900
Didn't know you were such a romantic.

441
00:22:31,420 --> 00:22:33,330
If you don't want
anything to happen to Songge,

442
00:22:33,420 --> 00:22:34,820
then get the money ready quickly.

443
00:22:39,780 --> 00:22:40,620
Ten thousand yuan.

444
00:22:40,960 --> 00:22:42,240
Not a penny less.

445
00:22:42,500 --> 00:22:43,340
Otherwise,

446
00:22:43,980 --> 00:22:44,820
your dad,

447
00:22:45,460 --> 00:22:46,300
the invalid,

448
00:22:46,300 --> 00:22:47,140
and you,

449
00:22:48,010 --> 00:22:49,090
you'll all die.

450
00:23:00,900 --> 00:23:03,620
(Yingxiong Roller Skating Rink)

451
00:24:07,780 --> 00:24:08,940
Think about your dad.

452
00:24:09,940 --> 00:24:11,060
Think about your invalid.

453
00:24:12,540 --> 00:24:13,660
Ten thousand yuan.

454
00:24:13,660 --> 00:24:14,940
Not a penny less.

455
00:24:27,700 --> 00:24:28,620
Chen Hui!

456
00:24:29,780 --> 00:24:31,180
Chen Hui, where are you?

457
00:24:32,580 --> 00:24:33,420
Chen Hui!

458
00:24:34,740 --> 00:24:35,680
- Songge!
- Chen Hui!

459
00:24:36,540 --> 00:24:37,380
I'm over here.

460
00:24:37,960 --> 00:24:38,900
How are you?

461
00:24:39,220 --> 00:24:40,160
It's all settled.

462
00:24:40,710 --> 00:24:41,610
Where's Lu Yuan?

463
00:24:41,610 --> 00:24:42,610
He took the money and left.

464
00:24:45,380 --> 00:24:46,220
Hui,

465
00:24:46,780 --> 00:24:47,820
you scared me to death.

466
00:24:48,980 --> 00:24:49,860
I thought...

467
00:24:51,460 --> 00:24:53,410
I thought you were going
to do something foolish.

468
00:24:53,620 --> 00:24:54,460
How could I?

469
00:24:55,780 --> 00:24:58,980
Like you said, we'll just consider it
paying for our peace of mind.

470
00:25:00,900 --> 00:25:01,740
It's my fault.

471
00:25:02,820 --> 00:25:04,620
I didn't handle it well
and made you worry.

472
00:25:04,820 --> 00:25:05,900
How could I blame you?

473
00:25:07,100 --> 00:25:08,380
It was my own carelessness

474
00:25:08,380 --> 00:25:09,680
that let him see my face.

475
00:25:09,680 --> 00:25:10,550
It's alright.

476
00:25:10,550 --> 00:25:11,470
It's over now.

477
00:25:11,470 --> 00:25:12,910
Everything's settled, so don't worry.

478
00:25:14,690 --> 00:25:16,010
Why are you back so soon?

479
00:25:16,180 --> 00:25:17,660
Doesn't dialysis take over four hours?

480
00:25:18,500 --> 00:25:19,440
I was worried about you,

481
00:25:19,860 --> 00:25:20,700
so I didn't do it

482
00:25:20,700 --> 00:25:21,780
and I just rushed back.

483
00:25:21,780 --> 00:25:22,660
That won't do.

484
00:25:22,660 --> 00:25:23,810
You can't skip dialysis.

485
00:25:23,990 --> 00:25:24,860
Come on.

486
00:25:24,860 --> 00:25:26,110
I'll go with you for your dialysis.

487
00:25:46,940 --> 00:25:48,180
(Fengyang Police Station)

488
00:25:48,700 --> 00:25:49,540
Director Chen.

489
00:25:50,420 --> 00:25:51,260
Chief Liu.

490
00:25:51,690 --> 00:25:53,090
Why didn't you get some rest

491
00:25:53,340 --> 00:25:54,500
when you went back this time?

492
00:25:54,500 --> 00:25:55,340
I'm fine now.

493
00:25:55,340 --> 00:25:56,540
The lab report is out.

494
00:25:57,710 --> 00:25:58,550
Good, have a seat.

495
00:26:02,220 --> 00:26:03,860
Besides Kejianin, Zhu Qiang's blood

496
00:26:03,860 --> 00:26:05,100
(Jiangbin Municipal People's Hospital Lab Report)
did contain components of stomach medicine.

497
00:26:05,420 --> 00:26:06,260
Right.

498
00:26:06,260 --> 00:26:07,340
When I was coming back,

499
00:26:07,340 --> 00:26:09,180
I made a special call to the hospital
to ask about it.

500
00:26:09,180 --> 00:26:10,720
There's nothing wrong
with Zhu Qiang's stomach.

501
00:26:10,730 --> 00:26:11,840
He's never taken any medicine.

502
00:26:12,260 --> 00:26:13,120
That means

503
00:26:13,120 --> 00:26:15,260
someone secretly put this stuff

504
00:26:15,260 --> 00:26:16,580
into the cough syrup

505
00:26:16,580 --> 00:26:17,420
and gave it to him.

506
00:26:18,100 --> 00:26:20,060
Yu Susu gave
the cough syrup to Zhu Qiang, right?

507
00:26:20,060 --> 00:26:21,500
Then she wanted to drive him mad.

508
00:26:21,510 --> 00:26:22,700
She was murdering her husband.

509
00:26:22,970 --> 00:26:24,670
Why would Yu Susu
want to harm Zhu Qiang?

510
00:26:24,950 --> 00:26:26,060
And who killed her?

511
00:26:29,420 --> 00:26:30,260
Master,

512
00:26:30,260 --> 00:26:31,620
do you think there's a possibility

513
00:26:33,220 --> 00:26:34,780
that Chi Huabo has been lying to us

514
00:26:34,780 --> 00:26:35,750
from the very beginning?

515
00:26:36,140 --> 00:26:38,060
Yu Susu never blackmailed him at all.

516
00:26:38,190 --> 00:26:39,730
Then, why did Yu Susu harm Zhu Qiang?

517
00:26:39,730 --> 00:26:41,420
So she could be with Chi Huabo.

518
00:26:41,500 --> 00:26:42,720
Chi Huabo found out about it,

519
00:26:43,060 --> 00:26:45,470
and fearing he'd be implicated,
he killed Yu Susu.

520
00:26:45,900 --> 00:26:47,220
Are you stupid?

521
00:26:47,980 --> 00:26:49,530
If Chi Huabo was afraid

522
00:26:49,530 --> 00:26:51,720
that Yu Susu killing Zhu Qiang
would implicate him,

523
00:26:51,790 --> 00:26:53,550
would he then dare to kill Yu Susu?

524
00:26:54,000 --> 00:26:55,680
Wouldn't that be an even greater crime?

525
00:26:55,920 --> 00:26:57,460
Can you use your brain?

526
00:26:58,540 --> 00:27:01,050
We questioned the two people
most closely related to Yu Susu.

527
00:27:01,300 --> 00:27:03,130
One is Chi Huabo,
and the other is Zhu Qiang.

528
00:27:03,450 --> 00:27:04,610
Both of them claimed

529
00:27:04,610 --> 00:27:06,410
they had never seen
that commemorative coin.

530
00:27:06,750 --> 00:27:08,400
Then who gave the commemorative coin

531
00:27:08,400 --> 00:27:09,240
found on Yu Susu?

532
00:27:09,350 --> 00:27:10,500
And what is the relationship

533
00:27:10,500 --> 00:27:12,650
between Yu Susu
and the middle-aged woman

534
00:27:12,710 --> 00:27:13,940
who got the commemorative coin?

535
00:27:16,180 --> 00:27:17,740
Yu Susu killing Zhu Qiang...

536
00:27:19,340 --> 00:27:20,870
Perhaps there's another motive.

537
00:27:22,860 --> 00:27:23,700
What motive?

538
00:27:25,620 --> 00:27:27,300
I suddenly thought of someone.

539
00:27:30,060 --> 00:27:31,820
We should go and ask him.

540
00:27:32,820 --> 00:27:34,300
(Jiangbin Municipal
People's Hospital Lab Report)

541
00:27:34,530 --> 00:27:36,610
Hongbing, I'm right
in the middle of a massage.

542
00:27:36,610 --> 00:27:37,450
You're so...

543
00:27:37,900 --> 00:27:38,740
Forget the massage.

544
00:27:38,740 --> 00:27:39,650
Forget the bath.

545
00:27:39,650 --> 00:27:40,960
Come here, hurry up.

546
00:27:41,050 --> 00:27:41,990
Let me introduce you.

547
00:27:42,420 --> 00:27:43,690
This is my friend, Huang Liang.

548
00:27:43,780 --> 00:27:44,970
This is Chief Liu

549
00:27:45,140 --> 00:27:46,180
from the municipal PSB.

550
00:27:47,380 --> 00:27:48,420
Hello, Chief Liu.

551
00:27:48,420 --> 00:27:49,260
Hello.

552
00:27:49,580 --> 00:27:50,450
Alright.

553
00:27:50,450 --> 00:27:51,300
Have a seat.

554
00:27:51,900 --> 00:27:52,940
Director Chen,

555
00:27:52,940 --> 00:27:54,710
you called me here in such a hurry.

556
00:27:55,700 --> 00:27:56,660
What is this about?

557
00:27:56,660 --> 00:27:58,100
Your family has lived

558
00:27:58,100 --> 00:28:00,340
in Fengyang for generations.

559
00:28:00,340 --> 00:28:01,220
Do you still remember

560
00:28:01,220 --> 00:28:02,260
when we were kids,

561
00:28:02,260 --> 00:28:04,120
your father told us about something?

562
00:28:04,660 --> 00:28:06,020
He said some women

563
00:28:06,020 --> 00:28:08,140
specifically look for miners to marry.

564
00:28:08,460 --> 00:28:10,880
When the miners
have an accident underground,

565
00:28:11,160 --> 00:28:12,960
they go to the mine owner for money.

566
00:28:13,110 --> 00:28:14,260
You mean

567
00:28:14,260 --> 00:28:15,300
Death Benefit Bride.

568
00:28:15,940 --> 00:28:17,620
These are all things from the old days.

569
00:28:17,760 --> 00:28:19,080
Tell us more about it.

570
00:28:19,150 --> 00:28:20,660
What's the trick behind it?

571
00:28:20,660 --> 00:28:21,500
Yes.

572
00:28:21,500 --> 00:28:23,050
My father told me back then,

573
00:28:23,380 --> 00:28:24,660
at that time,

574
00:28:24,660 --> 00:28:26,630
the coal mines here in Fengyang

575
00:28:26,630 --> 00:28:28,170
were all owned by rich landlords.

576
00:28:28,170 --> 00:28:29,510
They were just illegal coal pits.

577
00:28:29,690 --> 00:28:31,240
Cave-ins happened all the time.

578
00:28:31,820 --> 00:28:32,980
Going down into the shafts

579
00:28:32,980 --> 00:28:34,220
was extremely dangerous.

580
00:28:34,660 --> 00:28:35,860
Some women

581
00:28:35,860 --> 00:28:38,280
would specifically look for those miners

582
00:28:38,280 --> 00:28:39,840
who were lonely old bachelors

583
00:28:39,860 --> 00:28:40,740
and marry them.

584
00:28:40,740 --> 00:28:41,730
If nothing happened,

585
00:28:42,060 --> 00:28:43,540
they'd just live their lives together.

586
00:28:43,650 --> 00:28:44,950
But if an accident occurred,

587
00:28:45,340 --> 00:28:46,660
she would extort the owner.

588
00:28:46,940 --> 00:28:49,550
This way of marrying among these women

589
00:28:49,820 --> 00:28:51,210
was called "Death Benefit Bride."

590
00:28:51,750 --> 00:28:54,010
Were there any Death Benefit Brides
who secretly killed their husbands

591
00:28:54,100 --> 00:28:55,340
for the money?

592
00:28:55,340 --> 00:28:56,540
It seems there were.

593
00:28:56,540 --> 00:28:57,580
My father told me

594
00:28:57,580 --> 00:28:58,460
there was a woman

595
00:28:58,460 --> 00:28:59,960
who married six men in a row.

596
00:29:00,300 --> 00:29:01,540
Not long after they got married,

597
00:29:01,540 --> 00:29:03,220
those men died in the mine shafts.

598
00:29:03,340 --> 00:29:04,840
Later, the woman left with the money.

599
00:29:05,170 --> 00:29:06,900
I heard she even bought
a large courtyard

600
00:29:06,900 --> 00:29:07,990
in the provincial capital.

601
00:29:08,410 --> 00:29:09,950
But these are all legends from the past.

602
00:29:10,820 --> 00:29:12,190
Would anyone still do this today?

603
00:29:12,500 --> 00:29:13,370
Chief Liu,

604
00:29:13,370 --> 00:29:14,220
illegal coal pits

605
00:29:14,220 --> 00:29:15,380
don't have licenses.

606
00:29:15,540 --> 00:29:17,100
So if an accident happens underground,

607
00:29:17,200 --> 00:29:19,510
the mine owner will be sentenced.

608
00:29:19,670 --> 00:29:20,700
Because of that,

609
00:29:20,710 --> 00:29:22,880
everyone is willing
to pay for a private settlement.

610
00:29:23,620 --> 00:29:25,410
Since there is profit to be made,

611
00:29:26,300 --> 00:29:28,720
someone will be willing
to take the risk.

612
00:29:29,020 --> 00:29:31,110
Even if they'd be executed if caught,

613
00:29:31,220 --> 00:29:33,650
they are still willing
to do whatever it takes to get in.

614
00:29:35,380 --> 00:29:39,340
(Hemodialysis Room A)

615
00:29:50,100 --> 00:29:53,100
(Returning the call)

616
00:30:54,780 --> 00:30:55,800
Did you find her?

617
00:30:56,490 --> 00:30:58,330
I've contacted
the drug dealers from before.

618
00:30:59,060 --> 00:31:00,380
No one has seen that woman.

619
00:31:00,380 --> 00:31:01,940
So that means you didn't find her.

620
00:31:01,940 --> 00:31:03,050
Didn't I say?

621
00:31:03,130 --> 00:31:04,280
I've contacted everyone.

622
00:31:04,280 --> 00:31:05,190
No one knows her.

623
00:31:05,190 --> 00:31:06,210
Nobody knows her!

624
00:31:09,140 --> 00:31:10,300
What are you shouting for?

625
00:31:16,380 --> 00:31:18,140
Why are you so desperate to find her?

626
00:31:18,140 --> 00:31:19,140
Even if you find her,

627
00:31:19,140 --> 00:31:20,180
what can you do?

628
00:31:24,180 --> 00:31:25,260
Every time I find one,

629
00:31:26,740 --> 00:31:28,230
I will kill them.

630
00:31:30,460 --> 00:31:32,090
Everyone who deceived me

631
00:31:37,460 --> 00:31:38,880
must die.

632
00:31:51,230 --> 00:31:52,070
Mr. Huo,

633
00:31:53,020 --> 00:31:54,110
I have a way

634
00:31:54,260 --> 00:31:57,940
to help you find the person
you're looking for.

635
00:32:34,860 --> 00:32:35,860
Did Chen Hui send you?

636
00:32:57,220 --> 00:33:03,300
♪I always thought
once we see the full picture♪

637
00:33:04,620 --> 00:33:10,460
♪We could understand
each other with empathy♪

638
00:33:12,020 --> 00:33:18,460
♪I always thought
the path we never took♪

639
00:33:19,180 --> 00:33:24,780
♪Must have had more beautiful scenery♪

640
