♪Must have had more beautiful scenery♪

644
00:33:56,150 --> 00:33:59,060
♪Keep moving forward
and don't look back♪

645
00:33:59,890 --> 00:34:03,150
♪The shore is only reached
by the road ahead♪

646
00:34:03,600 --> 00:34:06,260
♪Too much debt has accumulated♪

647
